data.description: Welcome to 1712 Bremen! This cute home could be yours for the Holidays! Spacious living room offers original hardwood floors and loads of natural light! Eat-in kitchen has plenty of cabinet space! 2 great sized bedrooms feature hardwood floors as well! The lower level has new carpet, bar, and plenty of storage space! Outback you will find an oversized one car garage and a large yard! Call today for your private showing! Buyer to verify all MLS data.
